critical_positive: Our conversation went great. She was super friendly and we had a lot in common. critical_positive: We had a few shared experiences that we were able to connect on. And after we spoke about those familiar topics, it naturally led to other conversation avenues. For example, I live in Portland and he has family who live here... so we were able to talk about restaurants and the like.
critical_negative: I found that while we had some common experiences, he was slightly more reserved than myself (I tend to think of myself as more outgoing... an introverted extrovert if you will). That led me to feel as though I needed to come up with things to talk about to keep the conversation moving and being engaged. Whether that comes across when you view the footage, I don't know.
